<div class="panel-pane pane-custom pane-1" >
  
      
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <!--smart_paging_filter--><!--smart_paging_autop_filter--><h2 class="story-title">My Brother’s Secret</h2>  </div>

  
  </div>

<div class="panel-pane pane-entity-field pane-node-field-description" >
  
      
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <div class="field field-name-field-description field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Dale always wanted a traditional&nbsp;life with a traditional family. But he found&nbsp;happiness only when he decided to&nbsp;live and love the way he wanted—even if that&nbsp;meant hiding the truth about his sexuality&nbsp;from our parents, right up until his death.&nbsp;

&nbsp;
</div></div></div>  </div>

  
  </div>

<div class="panel-pane pane-contributor-list-pane" >
  
      
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <span class="frill">by</span> <a href="/contributor/w%E2%80%8Ak-stratton">W. K. Stratton</a>  </div>

  
  </div>

<div class="panel-pane pane-dynamic-date-pane" >
  
      
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <a href="/issue/february-2015">February 2015</a>  </div>

  
  </div>

<div class="panel-pane pane-content-share-pane" >
  
      
  
